com.paypal.paypalretailsdk

Class RetailInvoice

  • java.lang.Object
    • PayPalRetailObject
      • com.paypal.paypalretailsdk.Invoice
        • com.paypal.paypalretailsdk.RetailInvoice

  • public class RetailInvoice
extends Invoice
    The "Retail" Implementation of Invoice that is used by PPH only. Contains receiptDetails such as store ID, TerminalID, and countryCode. This class is a specific version implementation of the Invoice.
